### Response: Microsoft 365 Copilot demonstrates strong availability and performance for iterative writing tasks, with ongoing optimizations to minimize downtime.

Available: Copilot has been deployed at scale internally at Microsoft (330,000 employees), showing significant performance improvements and time savings for users completing iterative writing tasks. It leverages Azure's optimized AI infrastructure to process queries quickly, typically generating responses in seconds for standard prompts.

Planned: Microsoft continues to optimize Copilot's performance, with improvements like the new Teams client tuned to better accommodate Copilot with less lag.

These capabilities enable Copilot to maintain high availability and minimize downtime for iterative writing processes, with ongoing enhancements to improve reliability and performance.

